        <updateDate>2006-08-24T19:13:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p></p> <p></p> <p></p> <p></p> <p>Government Credit Card Abuse Prevention Act of 2006 - Directs each executive agency (with separate Department of Defense (DOD) requirements) and amends the Travel and Transportation Reform Act of 1998 to require specified credit card and convenience card controls and safeguards, including risk assessment analyses, audits, and the reporting of such analyses and audits.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
